Inspiring work. That different green and pink tint in different parts of the stage. Elements of the set design. That light setup, its movement and flickering. That music. That amazing voice of meesha and support musicians. and that beautiful combination all the elements. and that exceptional camera work and editing. congrats to each every person who was part of this.

As a photographer, i wished i was there to have taken shots during the production. Truly sensational.
